result.execSummary:
The defendant Frank Mosley III was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Frank Mosley III is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Frank Mosley III was found guilty of Armed Robbery [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime, Repeater], a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 943.32(2).
  • Frank Mosley III was found guilty of Armed Robbery [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime, Repeater], a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 943.32(2).
